Sekarang peluruku habis.

250
00:20:26,461 --> 00:20:27,921
T minus lima menit, Sayang.

251
00:20:40,475 --> 00:20:42,477
Lindsay, berpeganglah padaku.

252
00:21:03,832 --> 00:21:05,167
Luther!

253
00:21:05,916 --> 00:21:07,251
Kita pergi!

254
