256
00:21:38,199 --> 00:21:40,367
Lindsey! Ayo ke helikopter.

257
00:21:40,493 --> 00:21:42,036
Zhen, singkirkan truk itu.

258
00:21:42,119 --> 00:21:43,496
Ayo pergi!

259
00:21:50,044 --> 00:21:52,880
Ya Tuhan! Apa itu?
Kau tak bisa dengar itu?

260
00:21:53,339 --> 00:21:55,716
- Ya Tuhan!
