266
00:22:35,380 --> 00:22:36,923
Sakit sekali.

267
00:22:38,091 --> 00:22:40,385
Matikan itu. Kumohon.

268
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:58,778
Kumohon, Ethan.

269
00:23:04,033 --> 00:23:05,743
NITROGLISERIN - NITRAT MAGNESIUM

270
00:23:09,789 --> 00:23:12,125
Teman-teman, rudal
