00:23:52,540 --> 00:23:55,251
Ethan! Apa itu? Apa mereka
pasang sesuatu di kepalaku?

277
00:23:55,335 --> 00:23:57,294
Kau disuntikkan bom waktu.

278
00:23:57,377 --> 00:23:58,921
